$interpreted: Lizard General: Stop right there!
Misa: Get out of my way, I've got to find Joshua...! I'll explain when I get back!
Lizard General: Hmph. Explain?
Lizard General: Sinner of the shrine, haven't you done enough already!?
Lizard General: You fake. Now that your master is gone, you've got no powers. Get 'er!
Misa: I said, don't get in my way——!
Doubtful Soldier: Hey, didn't you say she was a fake? Her power seems pretty real...
Wavering Soldier: Actually, a lot of people still believe she's the Holy Maiden. She's just too young. She got tricked by Devious, that's all.
Doubtful Soldier: Who should I believe...
Misa: Found you!
Jahan: We only let you go 'cuz you're so cute. You must really want to die, is that it!?
Misa: ...*cough*...*cough*...let Joshua go!
Jahan: Hold on, now. I'm just kidding around!
Jahan: Oh no, wouldn't want to hurt your little hand!
Misa: Disgusting! You could be my grandfather!
Jahan: Hey! I'm not that old! Don't you dare say that about me!
Misa: Why do you want to hurt Joshua!?
Jahan: Joshua?
Jahan: Ah, so that's the twerp's name.
Misa: You don't know each other?
Jahan: I saw him at the Oasis Casino, talking 'biz with Yusuf, that's all.
Jahan: Don't know how he got Devious' recipe for the drugs. All you need to do is tweak it a bit, and that stuff could make some real money in other places~
Misa: Joshua knows how to make the medicine!?
Jahan: Interested? Wanna come back to my hometown with me?
Jahan: The stud you see before you almost had a factory built. If I succeed this time around, we'll be living the good life~
Jahan: Don't worry, you've got real potential. I can wait~
Misa: Don't touch me, you brute!
Misa: Ugh, what a weirdo.
Misa: Where's Joshua?
Misa: The High Priest's medicine...!
